headline.main: AFGHANS TO OUST AXIS NATIONALS; Approximately 200 Germans and Italians Will Receive British Safe Transit MOVE CLOSES ALLIED GAP It Follows the Soviet-British Demarche on Kabul After Action in Iran

lead_paragraph: LONDON, Oct. 19 -- Following friendly representations by the British and Russian Governments, news has been received here from Afghanistan that the government in Kabul has decided to expel all Germans and Italians in residence in the country.
abstract: Afghanistan yields to Brit-USSR request to oust Axis natls; Brit pledges safe transit; map
